Description: This is a beautiful Flamed Green with Gold Hardware. I have upgraded some of the old rusted out pieces. It looks great now. Made during the "Golden Era" of Ibanez in Korea 1996 and sounds great! This is very good shape. There are a couple dings and swirls. I was going to get them fixed for next to nothing, but don't have the time. Have to many guitars and need space for a new one. Comes with Hard case. Below are specs and some history. The S470FM is an S series solid body electric guitar model introduced by Ibanez in 1996. The S470FM features a mahogany body with a flamed maple top bolted to a maple Wizard II neck with a 22-fret rosewood fingerboard with dot position markers. Components include a double locking tremolo bridge, a locking nut and Ibanez pickups.
